<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">How could it possibly <a href=3D"https://link.=
mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34672373.259366/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZnQuY29tL2=
NvbnRlbnQvNTFjNTFhNmQtNDcyNy00MTNjLTk4ZjktNDU4YWZkZjUxZWQw/607f07ceef4b8524=
